\par The reason behind Qarun\rquote s hubris and his inability to fear Allah, was his wealth. He had forgotten that all wealth 
belongs to Allah and if He wished He could reclaim this wealth. Instead, he imagined that these treasures had been acquired by him as a result of his own abilities.
